## 복습과제
    - 1. 예배가 기쁨이 넘치는 찬양으로 성삼위 하나님께 영광을 돌리는데 집중해야 하는 두 가지 주요 이유는 무엇인가?
        * God is spirit, and his worshipers must worship in the Spirit and in truth. (John 4:24)
        * Suddenly a great company of the heavenly host appeared with the angel, praising God and saying, 
        “Glory to God in the highest heaven, and on earth peace to those on whom his favor rests.”(Luke 2:13-14)
        * Whoever believes in me, as Scripture has said, rivers of living water will flow from within them.(John 7:38-39)
        * For none of us lives for ourselves alone, and none of us dies for ourselves alone. (Romans 14:7)

        